00:19:17.850 --> 00:19:21.270
rate in Finland to behave very
differently than the crime

00:19:21.270 --> 00:19:22.740
rate in the other countries.

00:19:22.740 --> 00:19:28.200
So because they had this really
major reform, and what you see

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:29.797
is not that change.

00:19:29.797 --> 00:19:32.130
This is what I'm trying to
make out of these graphs, not

00:19:32.130 --> 00:19:33.790
more than that.

00:19:33.790 --> 00:19:34.800
Yeah?

00:19:34.800 --> 00:19:37.492
AUDIENCE: What about Singapore?

00:19:37.492 --> 00:19:42.723
I understand that in there
the punishment is severe

00:19:42.723 --> 00:19:45.300
