So the community
courts, they're trying

00:44:04.520 --> 00:44:07.820
to use the authority
of the criminal process

00:44:07.820 --> 00:44:10.430
and the authority of
the judge in order

00:44:10.430 --> 00:44:17.300
to help people to
get all the help

00:44:17.300 --> 00:44:19.940
they need in order
to be rehabilitated.

00:44:19.940 --> 00:44:22.370
And they can be
rehabilitated from addiction.

00:44:22.370 --> 00:44:25.340
They can have a lot
of other issues.

00:44:25.340 --> 00:44:26.930
That can be lonely.

00:44:26.930 --> 00:44:30.920
They can have a lot of
debt they can't handle.

00:44:30.920 --> 00:44:33.230
So once you go to
the community court,

00:44:33.230 --> 00:44:34.640
which it's a regular court.

00:44:34.640 --> 00:44:36.560
It's in the court system.

00:44:36.560 --> 00:44:40.080
