to go in this,

00:44:43.430 --> 00:44:45.360
you get into a
really long process.

00:44:45.360 --> 00:44:49.110
It's usually somewhere
between a year and two years,

00:44:49.110 --> 00:44:53.040
very intensive, in which you
get all the support you want.

00:44:53.040 --> 00:44:56.900
So you have someone taking
care that you'd go to rehab,

00:44:56.900 --> 00:44:58.466
someone helping you
find employment,

00:44:58.466 --> 00:44:59.840
someone helping
you with the kids

00:44:59.840 --> 00:45:01.610
if you don't have
anywhere to put them,

00:45:01.610 --> 00:45:05.460
someone helping you with parents
guidance, whatever you need.

00:45:05.460 --> 00:45:08.960
So every person in
the community courts

00:45:08.960 --> 00:45:11.930
gets what he or she needs,
and there's actually

00:45:11.930 --> 00:45:15.140
a really big group of
different professionals

00:45:15.140 --> 00:45:17.300
there to help them
do what they need.

00:45:17.300 --> 00:45:19.490
And as long as they're
in this process

00:45:19.490 --> 00:45:22.010
and do what they need
to do with all the help

00:45:22.010 --> 00:45:26.200
they get, in the end the
case will be overturned

00:45:26.200 --> 00:45:31.050
or they get like no punishment
at all, something of this sort.

00:45:31.050 --> 00:45:34.460
So actually what they do
is they use the stress

00:45:34.460 --> 00:45:37.620
that this caused out of the
criminal process and the fear,

00:45:37.620 --> 00:45:40.670
and the fear that you might
go to prison, and all of this

00:45:40.670 --> 00:45:45.530
in order to gently push you into
a community that supports you

00:45:45.530 --> 00:45:48.080
and helps you try
to figure out what's

00:45:48.080 --> 00:45:49.700
the main problems you have.

00:45:49.700 --> 00:45:52.850
So another name for
the community court

00:45:52.850 --> 00:45:54.680
is problem solving courts.

00:45:54.680 --> 00:45:56.840
So the idea is
that the people who

00:45:56.840 --> 00:46:01.430
go there like break the
law because there are

00:46:01.430 --> 00:46:05.780
other underlying problems,
like the criminal involvement

00:46:05.780 --> 00:46:08.240
is only the peak of
the iceberg and we

00:46:08.240 --> 00:46:12.350
need to go down, figure,
OK, why was she or he doing

00:46:12.350 --> 00:46:16.310
what he did, and there's
actually a very good success

00:46:16.310 --> 00:46:17.030
rate.

00:46:17.030 --> 00:46:20.720
It's about two years old,
the project, so they're

00:46:20.720 --> 00:46:23.660
only the first
people coming out,

00:46:23.660 --> 00:46:28.070
