trust the system,

00:46:33.590 --> 00:46:38.700
that they trust the government
and the regime much more,

00:46:38.700 --> 00:46:42.590
and people are actually
managing to regain

00:46:42.590 --> 00:46:45.560
control over their lives
using the community court.

00:46:45.560 --> 00:46:49.100
So this is one thing that is
happening, is now actually

00:46:49.100 --> 00:46:52.670
increasing, so they will
be in each of the districts

00:46:52.670 --> 00:46:56.410
by the end of 2019, I think.

