So this is one reason why
everybody's in a hurry

00:54:27.410 --> 00:54:29.270
to reduce the prison system.

00:54:29.270 --> 00:54:31.880
And another important case
law to know that kind of

00:54:31.880 --> 00:54:36.650
helps this is an old case law
from 2009, which abolished

00:54:36.650 --> 00:54:38.850
