00:54:38.850 --> 00:54:41.690
One of the reasons that
costs, high rise in the US,

00:54:41.690 --> 00:54:45.980
was private prisons, and once
the option of private prisons

00:54:45.980 --> 00:54:50.270
was actually blocked in Israel
