00:54:50.270 --> 00:54:55.490
stopped the amount in
which the prisons can rise,

00:54:55.490 --> 00:54:58.370
because it's really expensive
to build a public prison.

00:54:58.370 --> 00:55:01.670
So just like, you
know, there are also

00:55:01.670 --> 00:55:06.990
these decisions
that kind of help,

00:55:06.990 --> 00:55:13.910
that kind of support all the
criminal justice reforms.

